&lt;h1 id=&#34;Alt-H1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Alt-H1&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Alt-H1&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Alt-H1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;Alt-H2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Alt-H2&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Alt-H2&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Alt-H2&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;Emphasis&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Emphasis&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Emphasis&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Emphasis&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;Emphasis, aka italics, with *asterisks* or _underscores_.

Strong emphasis, aka bold, with **asterisks** or __underscores__.

Combined emphasis with **asterisks and _underscores_**.

Strikethrough uses two tildes. ~~Scratch this.~~
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emphasis, aka italics, with &lt;em&gt;asterisks&lt;/em&gt; or &lt;em&gt;underscores&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong emphasis, aka bold, with &lt;strong&gt;asterisks&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;underscores&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
